@startuml
title Activity Diagram: Upload and Process SRS Document

|User|
start
:Enter project details;
:Select SRS document file\n(PDF or TXT);
:Click "Upload" button;

|System|
:Validate file format;
note right
  Supported formats:
  - PDF
  - TXT
end note

if (File format valid?) then (no)
  |User|
  :Show error: "Unsupported file type";
  stop
else (yes)
  |System|
  :Extract text from document;
  :Split text into chunks\n(1000 chars, 200 overlap);
  :Generate embeddings for chunks\n(via OpenAI API);
  :Store vectors in Supabase\n(project_vectors table);
  :Update project metadata\n(MongoDB);
  |User|
  :Show success message\n"Document processed successfully";
  :Redirect to project dashboard;
  stop
endif

@enduml

